==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Anim
<hw>A"ni*m⟦eacute⟧</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>anim⟦eacute⟧</ets> animated (from the insects that are entrapped in
it); or native name.]</ety> <def>A resin exuding from a tropical
American tree (<spn>Hymen⟦ae⟧a courbaril</spn>), and much used by
varnish makers.</def> <rj><au>Ure.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

